author: SomeOrdinaryGamers
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at the day I've been talking about for over a year. Windows 10 has served us well and finally it's time for it's support to sunset. Windows 11 remains the only supported option and not everyone can even upgrade to it, what's the alternative? Let's find out! Thanks for watching!
Like, Comment and Subscribe for more videos!
title: Tomorrow Is the End of Windows 10...
